* good2.sno -- sink words appear ONLY inside string literals or in
* full-line comments; the detector must not flag any of these:
* the literal words CODE, EVAL, APPLY, LOAD must not trigger.
        S1 = 'CODE(this is data, not source)'
        S2 = "EVAL(also data) APPLY(still data) LOAD(libfoo)"
        OUTPUT = S1 ' / ' S2
END
